data.text:
Hey Hey welcome back to Friday!

Today’s artist continuing with our journey into Trans Country Music is singer and staff writer for Country Queer Mya Byrne! Byrne’s been bubbling under the radar for a few decades now racking up critical accolades.

That’s all she wrote! Have a good Friday and remember to follow the rules
